                                      Table « public.companies »
       Colonne        |            Type             | Collationnement | NULL-able |    Par défaut     
----------------------+-----------------------------+-----------------+-----------+-------------------
 id                   | uuid                        |                 | not null  | gen_random_uuid()
 name                 | character varying(255)      |                 | not null  | 
 slug                 | character varying(255)      |                 | not null  | 
 description          | text                        |                 |           | 
 logo_url             | text                        |                 |           | 
 primary_color        | character varying(7)        |                 |           | 
 secondary_color      | character varying(7)        |                 |           | 
 phone                | character varying(20)       |                 |           | 
 whatsapp             | character varying(20)       |                 |           | 
 facebook_url         | text                        |                 |           | 
 headquarters_address | text                        |                 |           | 
 rating_average       | numeric(3,1)                |                 |           | 0.0
 total_ratings        | integer                     |                 |           | 0
 is_active            | boolean                     |                 |           | true
 created_at           | timestamp without time zone |                 |           | CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
 updated_at           | timestamp without time zone |                 |           | CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
Index :
    "companies_pkey" PRIMARY KEY, btree (id)
    "companies_slug_key" UNIQUE CONSTRAINT, btree (slug)
    "idx_companies_active" btree (is_active)
    "idx_companies_rating" btree (rating_average DESC)
    "idx_companies_slug" btree (slug)
Référencé par :
    TABLE "admin_users" CONSTRAINT "admin_users_company_id_fkey" FOREIGN KEY (company_id) REFERENCES companies(id) ON DELETE SET NULL
    TABLE "bookings" CONSTRAINT "bookings_company_id_fkey" FOREIGN KEY (company_id) REFERENCES companies(id)
    TABLE "lines" CONSTRAINT "lines_company_id_fkey" FOREIGN KEY (company_id) REFERENCES companies(id) ON DELETE CASCADE
    TABLE "promo_codes" CONSTRAINT "promo_codes_company_id_fkey" FOREIGN KEY (company_id) REFERENCES companies(id) ON DELETE SET NULL
    TABLE "ratings" CONSTRAINT "ratings_company_id_fkey" FOREIGN KEY (company_id) REFERENCES companies(id) ON DELETE CASCADE
Triggers :
    companies_update_timestamp BEFORE UPDATE ON companies FOR EACH ROW EXECUTE FUNCTION update_timestamp()
    update_companies_updated_at BEFORE UPDATE ON companies FOR EACH ROW EXECUTE FUNCTION update_updated_at_column()

